            <span class="block">HOW AI</span>
            <span class="block text-[#6366F1] mt-2">BUILDERS WORK</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 font-medium max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
            Under the hood of AI website generation. No marketing fluff—technical reality from reverse engineering 12 AI builders.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-indigo-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-black">12</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">Builders Analyzed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-indigo-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
