          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">AI website builders use multiple AI technologies: <strong class="text-indigo-600">Natural Language Processing (NLP)</strong> to understand user requirements, <strong class="text-indigo-600">Large Language Models (LLM)</strong> like GPT for content generation, <strong class="text-indigo-600">Machine Learning</strong> for template matching and recommendations, <strong class="text-indigo-600">Computer Vision</strong> for image selection and optimization, <strong class="text-indigo-600">Pattern Recognition</strong> for industry-specific design, and <strong class="text-indigo-600">Predictive Analytics</strong> for user experience optimization. These technologies work together to transform simple text input into complete, professional websites.</p>
        </div>
