          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">AI-generated websites are unique based on your input. While they may start from templates, the AI customizes content, layout, colors, images, and styling based on your specific requirements. Different inputs produce different results. Additionally, visual editing tools allow you to further customize and differentiate your site. Modern AI builders have massive template databases and sophisticated customization algorithms that ensure variety. However, <strong class="text-indigo-600">heavy customization using the editor is recommended for maximum uniqueness</strong>. Template-based generation means similar inputs may produce similar results across different users—your job is to customize enough to stand out.</p>
